      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUCebf4607825f310058ad892b8834c33d2"></a>Installation of the connecting rod assembly
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e18140"> </a>Install the connecting rod assembly (1) and (2) in the crankcase half, carry out the shimming and crankcase half reassembly
            procedure as described in Section&nbsp;"<a href="45230.html#DUC54da126825b810058735b8c023d015d2">Reassembling the crankcase halves</a>".
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="Attenzione"><img class="Attenzione" width="28" height="25" style="display: inline; float: none; left: 0.0; text-align: left; top: 0.0;" src="img/important.jpg">Important
      </div>
      <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e18146"> </a>Make sure that the connecting rods are correctly positioned in the relevant cylinder seats. Incorrect positioning of the connecting
         rods at this stage will inevitably lead to the need to re-open the crankcase half.
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_9_053302273.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e18151"> </a>Reassemble the crankcase halves (<a href="45230.html#DUC54da126825b810058735b8c023d015d2">Reassembling the crankcase halves</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e18156"> </a>Refit the mesh filter (<a href="77245.html#DUCc57ed0d029f510058c2bed44952c77d2">Changing engine oil and filter cartridge</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e18161"> </a>Refit the primary drive gear (<a href="45144.html#DUC41e9ea28257e100580b68e32a097eed2">Removing the primary drive gear</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e18166"> </a>Refit the oil pump (<a href="44904.html#DUCcbf54ac824f2100583a5b051d7198fd2">Refitting the oil pump</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e18171"> </a>Refit the clutch unit (<a href="45128.html#DUCafa47568257b10058cb2f04d994144d2">Refitting the clutch</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e18176"> </a>Refit the clutch cover (<a href="45142.html#DUC71320cb8257c10058cbcf04d994144d2">Refitting the clutch cover</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e18181"> </a>Refit the starter motor (<a href="45213.html#DUCc8b137a826841005887ee38e40fd97d2">Refitting the starter motor</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e18186"> </a>Refit the generator and its cover (<a href="45184.html#DUCe2a16b98259310058919eb60359b4bd2">Refitting the flywheel/generator unit</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e18191"> </a>Refit the cylinder/piston assembly (<a href="45120.html#DUC24353f28257910058ca3f04d994144d2">Refitting the cylinder/piston assembly</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e18196"> </a>Refit the complete cylinder head unit (<a href="45101.html#DUC9e3e589025291005853db664ff2668d2">Reassembling the cylinder head</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e18201"> </a>Refit the camshafts (<a href="45078.html#DUC388127a0256810058981df0f9b3366d2">Refitting the camshafts</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e18207"> </a>Refit the timing components (<a href="45054.html#DUC2edb28d02519100584b1d8c3784850d2">Refitting the head pulleys/idler tensioners</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e18212"> </a>Install the engine in the frame (<a href="44896.html#DUCbe26f6e024f1100583a1b051d7198fd2">Refitting the engine</a>).
         </div>
      </div>
